android.os.Build.MODEL; - po ovome ce se gledaju rankings i na obicnom UI-ju moze isto
kad s eklikne host izadje toast text kao napravljen srever



Drawable
Ovo je gde se prave custom button background...

Shape Drawables: Define custom shapes like rectangles, circles, etc.

State List Drawables: Handle different states (pressed, focused, etc.) for UI elements.

Image Resources: Store bitmap images (PNG, JPG, etc.).

Nine Patch Images: Stretchable images, perfect for backgrounds or UI elements.

Vector Drawables: Scalable vector images, great for icons and simple graphics.

Animation Drawables: Frame-by-frame image animations.

Layer List Drawables: Combine multiple drawables into one.